videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright hits a three to cap a 9-0 run to give the Wildcats an 11-4 lead.
videos.headline: Arizona's Jackson-Cartwright hits corner 3

videos.description: Emmanuel Akot hits a corner 3-pointer to extend the Wildcats lead to 22-8.
videos.headline: Arizona's Akot nails buzzer-beating 3

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright grabs the rebound and goes coast-to-coast to score with a right-handed layup for Arizona.
videos.headline: Jackson-Cartwright races the floor for layup

videos.description: Allonzo Trier hits a 3-pointer just in time for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier beats the shot clock with 3

videos.description: Mason Riggins receives a no-look pass from Deishuan Booker who finishes with a powerful dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Long Beach State's Booker and Riggins combine for dunk

videos.description: Ira Lee gets the rebound and runs the length of the court for a layup to extend the lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Arizona's Lee goes coast-to-coast for layup

videos.description: Ira Lee blocks Long Beach State's KJ Byers shot and saves the ball to give possession back to Arizona.
videos.headline: Lee with resistance at the rim
